data.description: A MUST-SEE home with NO HOA and great proximity to shopping, dining, schools, and the Vintage Park area!  This lovely two-story home has had many updates throughout!  NEW Granite countertops 2023, NEW ceiling fans, all NEW lighting and mirrors in the bathrooms, NEW kitchen sink and faucet 2023, NEW AC 2023, NEW sprinkler system 2023, vinyl plank flooring on the stairs and throughout the second story 2020, NEW garage door opener 2023, and more!  Great bedroom spaces upstairs with two full bathrooms up and a half bath down.  Plenty of counter and cabinet space in the kitchen, and head out to the backyard and see the cute, covered porch complete with a ceiling fan, lights, and tv!  Gutters installed on the home as well. The owner has poured into the details of this well-maintained home so schedule your tour today!
